### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@gmail.com",
  "password": "inge123456",
  "preferences": ["fiction", "history"],
  "annualGoal": 24
}

### Login with existing user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@gmail.com",
  "password": "inge123456"
}
